OL,3,CAlderney 'living beyond its means'
OL,4,Cwarns senior politician
OL,6,FAlderney's senior politician has
OL,7,Fwarned the island is "living beyond
OL,8,Fits means", despite the island's
OL,9,Fbudget reporting a surplus.
OL,11,FPolicy and Finance Chair, Nigel
OL,12,FVooght, presented the island's budget
OL,13,Fto the States of Guernsey today
OL,14,F(Wednesday 16 October).
OL,16,FThe warning comes despite a #400,000
OL,17,Fsurplus in this year's forecast, which
OL,18,Fmeans Alderney Property Tax and water
OL,19,Frates won't increase this year.
