OL,3,CAlderney 'living beyond its means'
OL,4,Cwarns senior politician
OL,6,FFuel duty will also remain consistent
OL,7,Fwith the States of Guernsey rate for
OL,8,F2025.
OL,10,FHowever, the cost of transferred
OL,11,Fservices including healthcare and
OL,12,Feducation continues to exceed the
OL,13,Ftaxes paid to Guernsey's treasury.
OL,15,FMr Vooght warns: "Despite delivering
OL,16,Fthis balanced budget, we must be
OL,17,Fconscious of the simple fact that
OL,18,FAlderney is living beyond its means.
